<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>夏天很快就过去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>叶子开始从树上掉落。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘很累，她的衣服也破了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘在地上发现了一些坚果。她捡起了一颗小的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，这是我的！”一只松鼠大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我先找到它的。”拇指姑娘坚持说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，你好像也是在做过冬的准备哦。”那只松鼠回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冬天？”拇指姑娘说，“那是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>松鼠很惊讶，摇了摇尾巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冬天就是很冷的时候，笨蛋。”松鼠说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那时很难找到食物。你需要搜集食物储存起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我现在就在做这件事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>松鼠拿起另一个坚果，快速地跑到树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天气渐渐变冷。食物也很难找到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，拇指姑娘又饿又累，她睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她梦到自己在一个温暖的床上。美妙的声音在唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘醒了。她没有在做梦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在哪里？”她揉了揉自己的眼睛问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你很安全，亲爱的。”一只鸟儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘站了起来。她在一个鸟巢里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们觉得你需要帮助。所以我们把你带到我们家里了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸟儿说，“我是麦琪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听到了美妙的声音。”拇指姑娘介绍完自己后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在唱歌。”另一只鸟说，“我的名字是克里斯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有很长时间没有唱歌了。”拇指姑娘说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以前高兴的时候也会唱歌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“并不是所有歌都是开心的歌。”麦琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么意思？”拇指姑娘问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>克里斯和麦琪看着对方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每一首歌都不一样，”克里斯说，“听听这一首。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的歌很短，他听上去很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你听起来不开心。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>克里斯点点头：“那是一首生气的歌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你再听听这一首？”麦琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的歌很慢很安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。”拇指姑娘说，“这是一首什么样的歌呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有问题需要解决的时候就会唱这首歌。”麦琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能教我一些歌吗？”拇指姑娘问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然可以。”麦琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们教了拇指姑娘很多鸟的歌曲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每一首歌都很特别。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是有一种歌是一种秘密的语言。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这种歌是像说话的歌，拇指姑娘也学习了这些歌曲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘和她的朋友麦琪和克里斯待在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸟儿们给了她吃的，还为她保暖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是很快鸟儿们就得离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冬天快要到了。”麦琪说，“我们该飞到南方去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我多么希望我也有翅膀。”拇指姑娘伤心地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那样我就可以和你们一起飞走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸟儿们把她放在地上，然后唱了一首再见的歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，拇指姑娘。”他们说，“你会找到家的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，朋友们。”她回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>克里斯和麦琪飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>